{"id":285,"parent_id":266,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":285,"title":"Revelation 19","subtitle":"","short_title":"Rev.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 19"],[".studySummary",["i","The marriage supper of the Lamb is made ready—The testimony of Jesus is the spirit of prophecy—Christ is King of Kings and Lord of Lords."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.1","order":"03.29.019.28294"},["b","1"],"And after these things I heard a great voice of much people in heaven, saying, Alleluia; Salvation, and glory, and honour, and power, unto the Lord our God:"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.2","order":"03.29.019.28295"},["b","2"],"For true and righteous",["i","are"],"his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"judgments"],": for he hath",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"judged"],"the great",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"whore"],", which did corrupt the earth with her fornication, and hath avenged the blood of his servants at her hand."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.3","order":"03.29.019.28296"},["b","3"],"And again they said, Alleluia. And her",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"smoke"],"rose up for ever and ever."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.4","order":"03.29.019.28297"},["b","4"],"And the four and twenty elders and the four",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"beasts"],"fell down and worshipped God that sat on the throne, saying, Amen; Alleluia."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.5","order":"03.29.019.28298"},["b","5"],"And a voice came out of the throne, saying, Praise our God, all ye his servants, and ye that fear him, both small and great."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.6","order":"03.29.019.28299"},["b","6"],"And I heard as it were the voice of a great multitude, and as the voice of many waters, and as the voice of mighty thunderings, saying, Alleluia: for the Lord",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"God"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"omnipotent"],"reigneth."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.7","order":"03.29.019.28300"},["b","7"],"Let us be glad and rejoice, and give honour to him: for the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"marriage"],"of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"Lamb"],"is come, and his wife hath made herself ready."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.8","order":"03.29.019.28301"},["b","8"],"And to her was granted that she should be arrayed in fine linen, clean and white: for the fine",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"linen"],"is the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"righteousness"],"of saints."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.9","order":"03.29.019.28302"},["b","9"],"And he saith unto me, Write, Blessed",["i","are"],"they which are called unto the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"marriage"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"supper"],"of the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"Lamb"],". And he saith unto me, These are the true sayings of God."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.10","order":"03.29.019.28303"},["b","10"],"And I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"fell"],"at his feet to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"worship"],"him. And he said unto me, See",["i","thou do it"],"not: I am thy",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"fellowservant"],", and of thy brethren that have the testimony of Jesus: worship God: for the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"testimony"],"of Jesus is the spirit of",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_10e"},"prophecy"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.11","order":"03.29.019.28304"},["b","11"],"And I saw heaven opened, and behold a white horse; and he that sat upon him",["i","was"],"called Faithful and True, and in righteousness he doth",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"judge"],"and make",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"war"],"."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.12","order":"03.29.019.28305"},["b","12"],"His",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"eyes"],["i","were"],"as a flame of fire, and on his head",["i","were"],"many crowns; and he had a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"name"],"written, that no man knew, but he himself."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.13","order":"03.29.019.28306"},["b","13"],"And he",["i","was"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"clothed"],"with a vesture dipped in blood: and his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"name"],"is called The",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"Word of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.14","order":"03.29.019.28307"},["b","14"],"And the armies",["i","which were"],"in heaven followed him upon white horses,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"clothed"],"in fine linen, white and clean."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.15","order":"03.29.019.28308"},["b","15"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"And"],"out of his mouth goeth a sharp sword, that with it he should smite the nations: and he shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"rule"],"them with a rod of iron: and he treadeth the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"winepress"],"of the fierceness and wrath of Almighty God."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.16","order":"03.29.019.28309"},["b","16"],"And he hath on",["i","his"],"vesture and on his thigh a name written,",["span.allCaps",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"King of Kings"],", and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"Lord"],"of Lords"],"."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.17","order":"03.29.019.28310"},["b","17"],"And I saw an angel standing in the sun; and he cried with a loud voice, saying to all the fowls that fly in the midst of heaven, Come and gather yourselves together unto the supper of the great God;"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.18","order":"03.29.019.28311"},["b","18"],"That ye may eat the flesh of kings, and the flesh of captains, and the flesh of mighty men, and the flesh of horses, and of them that sit on them, and the flesh of all",["i",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"men"],", both"],"free and bond, both small and great."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.19","order":"03.29.019.28312"},["b","19"],"And I saw the beast, and the kings of the earth, and their armies, gathered together to make war against him that sat on the horse, and against his army."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.20","order":"03.29.019.28313"},["b","20"],"And the beast was taken, and with him the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"false prophet"],"that wrought",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"miracles"],"before him, with which he",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_20c"},"deceived"],"them that had received the mark of the beast, and them that worshipped his image. These both were cast alive into a",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_20d"},"lake"],"of",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_20e"},"fire"],"burning with brimstone."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.21","order":"03.29.019.28314"},["b","21"],"And the remnant were slain",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"with"],"the sword of him that sat upon the horse, which",["i","sword"],"proceeded out of his mouth: and all the fowls were filled with their flesh."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.2a","order":"03.29.019.28315"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-judge"},"TG Jesus Christ, Judge"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.2b","order":"03.29.019.28317"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/17.1.1-2"},"Rev. 17:1 (1–2)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.2c","order":"03.29.019.28319"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/29.21"},"D&C 29:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.3a","order":"03.29.019.28321"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/19.28"},"Gen. 19:28"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.4a","order":"03.29.019.28323"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cherubim"},"TG Cherubim"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.6a","order":"03.29.019.28325"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/2.47"},"Dan. 2:47"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.6b","order":"03.29.019.28327"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-power-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Power of"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.7a","order":"03.29.019.28329"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/54.5"},"Isa. 54:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.2.2-14"},"Matt. 22:2 (2–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/5.34"},"Luke 5:34"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/21.2"},"Rev. 21:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.7b","order":"03.29.019.28331"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-lamb-of-god"},"TG Jesus Christ, Lamb of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.8a","order":"03.29.019.28333"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.11.11-14"},"Matt. 22:11 (11–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/12.10.10-11"},"1 Ne. 12:10 (10–11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.8b","order":"03.29.019.28335"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/5.27"},"Alma 5:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.9a","order":"03.29.019.28337"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.11"},"D&C 58:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.9b","order":"03.29.019.28339"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/14.15"},"Luke 14:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/22.30"},"22:30"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.9c","order":"03.29.019.28341"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-lamb-of-god"},"TG Jesus Christ, Lamb of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.10a","order":"03.29.019.28343"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/22.8"},"Rev. 22:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.10b","order":"03.29.019.28345"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/worship"},"TG Worship"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.10c","order":"03.29.019.28347"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/10.26"},"Acts 10:26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/1.1.1-6"},"Rev. 1:1 (1–6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.10d","order":"03.29.019.28349"},["b","10d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/testimony"},"TG Testimony"],"."],["div",{"id":"10e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.10e","order":"03.29.019.28351"},["b","10e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophecy"},"TG Prophecy"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.11a","order":"03.29.019.28353"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-judge"},"TG Jesus Christ, Judge"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.11b","order":"03.29.019.28355"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/war"},"TG War"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.12a","order":"03.29.019.28357"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-manifestations-of"},"TG God, Manifestations of"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.12b","order":"03.29.019.28359"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/2.17.12-17"},"Rev. 2:17 (12–17)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.13a","order":"03.29.019.28361"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.2.2-3"},"Isa. 63:2 (2–3)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.48.48-51"},"D&C 133:48 (48–51)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.13b","order":"03.29.019.28363"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/name"},"TG Name"],"."],["div",{"id":"13c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.13c","order":"03.29.019.28365"},["b","13c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/1.32.32-33"},"Moses 1:32 (32–33)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-messenger-of-the-covenant"},"TG Jesus Christ, Messenger of the Covenant"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.14a","order":"03.29.019.28367"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/clothing"},"TG Clothing"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.15a","order":"03.29.019.28369"},["b","15a"],["span.small","JST"],"Rev. 19:15 And out of his mouth",["i","proceedeth the word of God, and"],"with it he",["i","will"],"smite the nations; and he",["i","will"],"rule them with",["i","the word of his mouth;"],"and he treadeth the winepress",["i","in"],"the fierceness and wrath of Almighty God.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/11.4"},"Isa. 11:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.15b","order":"03.29.019.28371"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-authority-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Authority of"],"."],["div",{"id":"15c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.15c","order":"03.29.019.28373"},["b","15c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.3.3-4"},"Isa. 63:3 (3–4)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/14.19.17-20"},"Rev. 14:19 (17–20)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/88.106"},"D&C 88:106"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.16a","order":"03.29.019.28375"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-second-coming"},"TG Jesus Christ, Second Coming"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.16b","order":"03.29.019.28377"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/10.17"},"Deut. 10:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/17.14"},"Rev. 17:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.18a","order":"03.29.019.28379"},["b","18a"],["span.small","JST"],"Rev. 19:18 …",["i","who fight against the Lamb,"],"both",["i","bond and"],"free, both small and great."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.20a","order":"03.29.019.28381"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/antichrist"},"TG Antichrist"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/false-prophets"},"False Prophets"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.20b","order":"03.29.019.28383"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/miracle"},"TG Miracle"],"."],["div",{"id":"20c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.20c","order":"03.29.019.28385"},["b","20c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/13.14.11-18"},"Rev. 13:14 (11–18)"],"."],["div",{"id":"20d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.20d","order":"03.29.019.28387"},["b","20d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.12"},"Matt. 8:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/13.42"},"13:42"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/112.24"},"D&C 112:24"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hell"},"TG Hell"],"."],["div",{"id":"20e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.20e","order":"03.29.019.28389"},["b","20e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/7.11"},"Dan. 7:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/19.21a","order":"03.29.019.28391"},["b","21a"],["span.small","JST"],"Rev. 19:21 … with the",["i","word"],"of him that sat upon the horse, which",["i","word"],"proceeded out of his mouth …"]]}
